l punishment, lacked a certain subtlety, &amp; besides, no one who’s working on building AI or talks about these things actually takes the original formulation seriously.</p><p>Roko’s Second Formulation of the Basilisk</p><a href="https://twitter.com/RokoMijic/status/1362832556001959936" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/mrYFxDfevAdGRPETnwK5wOjfCo1vQgjihTf0T7320Ag=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvdHdpdHRlcl9uYW1lL3dfOTYvUm9rb01pamljLmpwZw==" alt="Twitter avatar for @RokoMijic" loading="lazy"/>Roko.Eth @RokoMijicThere are two things that matter in life: 

