People will tell you lies about how there are other things that matter, and how well you do in life will depend on how well you resist those lies.</a><a href="https://twitter.com/RokoMijic/status/1362832556001959936" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">6:32 PM ∙ Feb 19, 2021223Likes29Retweets</a><p>Roko’s Basilisk, as it is more succinctly phrased by Roko eleven years later here, is realism &amp; the negation of the will itself. Fantasies of hellfire do not need to be present for men to tremble before a transcendental judgment of <em>you must, </em>if<em> </em>it is conceived as coming from “reality”. </p><p>But material reality, as an immanent thing, is not capable of passing transcendental judgments on man. All material reality shows us, all we can do is: articulate the dominant value structure of an existing social formation. </p><p>Roko has found the dominant outstanding systems of value &amp; presents it to Twitter saying “I have found the only value system which is objectively correct, I have determined that I must follow it exactly, in order to be less wrong than I am”. Many in the comment section argue with him &amp; try to tell him that he seems philosophically confused; he seems to not get it. The Basilisk’s venom has infected him, we consider the condition terminal. </p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0aff09e0-60b1-4b1a-b092-0884be290edf_704x704.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/vzT_v4gy5EkaJbHx_-z6jkkfPgKZNJlFd_2SkS6fJJU=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYwYWZmMDllMC02MGIxLTRiMWEtYjA5Mi0wODg0YmUy